OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783682372
OL,3,CFriend of 16-year-old boy stabbed saw
OL,4,Cattacker 'with no hesitation', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA friend of a 16-year-old boy stabbed
OL,8,Fat a train station said he saw the
OL,9,Fattacker pull a knife out "no words,
OL,10,Fno hesitation, he just did it", a
OL,11,Fcourt has heard.
OL,13,FA 16-year-old boy is on trial at Hove
OL,14,FCrown Court charged with the murder of
OL,15,FJoshua Ingram, who was fatally wounded
OL,16,Fat Seaford railway station in East
OL,17,FSussex, on September 10 2025.
OL,19,FThe defendant has pleaded guilty to an
OL,20,Falternative charge of manslaughter.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@^O]
