FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783682372
OL,3,CFriend of 16-year-old boy stabbed saw
OL,4,Cattacker 'with no hesitation', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FWhen the friend, who cannot be named
OL,8,Ffor legal reasons, saw the defendant
OL,9,Freach for an "army knife" with a black
OL,10,Fhandle, he screamed "Josh!", the court
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FIn a recorded police interview played
OL,14,Fto jurors, the friend told officers:
OL,15,F"Josh turned round, by the time he
OL,16,Fturned round he got stabbed."
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@YO]rD@UOUrD@[O]wD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
