FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783682372
OL,3,CFriend of 16-year-old boy stabbed saw
OL,4,Cattacker 'with no hesitation', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAsked about the defendant, he said:
OL,8,F"He had no hesitation, he had a very
OL,9,Fstill facial expression, he wasn't
OL,10,Fpulling a face, he didn't look like he
OL,11,Fhad anger in him.
OL,13,F"He looked very calm and just normal
OL,14,Fbut then just did that."
OL,16,FAsked if Joshua said anything to him,
OL,17,Fhe added: "I don't think Josh even
OL,18,Fknew what had happened."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUvD@XO]yD@KOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
