OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783682372
OL,3,CFriend of 16-year-old boy stabbed saw
OL,4,Cattacker 'with no hesitation', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe recalled seeing Joshua walk a
OL,8,Fcouple of steps and then "dropped to
OL,9,Fthe floor" as he asked Siri to call
OL,10,F999.
OL,12,F"I was so in shock I didn't know what
OL,13,Fto do."
OL,15,FBefore the incident, the teenager said
OL,16,Fhe was walking with Joshua to the
OL,17,Ftrain station and Joshua said: "Is
OL,18,Fthat (the defendant), I owe him #20."
OL,20,FBut the friend said: "He didn't say it
OL,21,Fin a worrying way.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@JO]tD@AOUuD@GO]yD@`OUzD@eO]|D@
OL,26,AVOU
