FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783682372
OL,3,CFriend of 16-year-old boy stabbed saw
OL,4,Cattacker 'with no hesitation', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"He said it in a normal tone, not
OL,8,Fthinking he was going to get stabbed,
OL,9,Fthinking (the defendant) was going to
OL,10,Fcome up and say 'where's my money?'."
OL,12,FThe 16-year-old defendant is also
OL,13,Faccused, along with two youths aged 17
OL,14,Fand 15, of conspiracy to cause GBH
OL,15,Fwith intent.
OL,17,FThe 15-year-old is also on trial
OL,18,Fcharged with assisting an offender,
OL,19,Fwhich the 17-year-old has pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
